  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high</p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, cook for 15 min or until almost fork tender (approx. step 7)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\n<p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and the <strong>juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong></p>\n<p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>chicken breast<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into strips and add them to the <strong>herby marinade</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p>\n<p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop them finely, discard the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-4-x700.jpg",
