    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong> to a baking tray and spoon over any <strong>remaining marinade </strong></p>\n<p>Put the tray under the grill for 7-10 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and beginning to brown – this<span class=\"text-highlight\"> is your <strong>grilled Greek-style chicken</strong></span></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2106.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
