            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> green beans</strong> in half</p>\n<p>Once the <strong>potatoes</strong> are almost cooked, add the <strong>chopped green beans</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 3-4 min under the beans are tender with a bite</p>\n<p>Once done, drain and return to the pot with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p>\n<p>Cut any <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
